  • Skin care: gentle wash + dry, moisturize, antimicrobial selected;
  • Hyperhidrosis: aluminum chloride, BoNT, oral;
  • Verrucous hyperplasia: total contact socket + treat underlying;
  • Contact dermatitis: change liner material, topical steroid;
  • Bursae: ice, NSAID, injection, surgical selected;

(5) Education: daily skin inspection, hygiene, sock management, weight stability, prosthesis off if sore;

(6) Team: prosthetist + physiatrist + PT + dermatology selected;

(7) Imaging/labs: if osteomyelitis suspected; Modern: 3D-scanning custom sockets + advanced liners + hygiene
