(7) Salience Matters: meaningful task engages plasticity better;

(8) Age Matters: training-induced plasticity occurs more readily in younger brains but throughout lifespan;

(9) Transference: plasticity in one brain pathway can enhance acquisition of similar behaviors;

(10) Interference: plasticity in one brain pathway can interfere w/ another;

