  • Peripheral (skeletal muscle): a-vO2 difference — mitochondrial density + capillary density + myoglobin + oxidative enzymes;
  • Pulmonary: rarely limiting except disease (diffusion, ventilation);
  • Hemoglobin/blood (CaO2);

