(4) Transition from pediatric (age 14+): gradual + planned + portable medical summary + adult-oriented;

(5) Functional optimization: PT + OT + SLP + cognitive support + adaptive equipment + community integration + vocational (supported employment) + recreation;

(6) Family caregiver — aging considerations: succession planning (future caregivers), special needs trust + financial, sibling involvement, adult day programs, group home transition planning, advance directives + GoC;

